---
import CaseStudy from '../../layouts/CaseStudy.astro';
---
<CaseStudy slug="pocn">
  <Fragment slot="header">
    <div class="cs-hero" style="border:0;padding:0;overflow:hidden"><img src="/Personal/Images/POCN/pocn-cs-gfx-1.jpg" alt="POCN case study graphic" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block" /></div>
    <div class="cs-tags"><span class="cs-tag">Performance</span><span class="cs-tag">Healthcare</span><span class="cs-tag">Programmatic</span><span class="cs-tag">HCP Marketing</span></div>
    <div class="cs-title">Driving Efficiency in Programmatic Media for Regulated Healthcare</div>
    <div class="cs-subtitle">Managed $1.7M+ in pharmaceutical media across 30+ concurrent HCP campaigns — driving compounding efficiency gains while consistently hitting contracted KPIs in a regulated environment.</div>
    <div class="cs-meta-card">
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Client</div><div class="cs-meta-value">POCN</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Duration</div><div class="cs-meta-value">May 2022 – Jul 2024 (26 months)</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Role</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Digital Marketing Manager</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Industry</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Healthcare / Pharma</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Clients</div><div class="cs-meta-value">J&amp;J · Lilly · AbbVie · Regeneron</div></div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="stat-strip">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">$1.7M+</div><div class="stat-label">Total media managed</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">30+</div><div class="stat-label">Concurrent campaigns at peak</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">50+</div><div class="stat-label">Pharmaceutical therapies supported</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Context · Action · Result</div>
    <div class="car-grid">
      <div class="car-sidebar">
        <div class="car-step active" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-1')"><div class="car-step-label">01 · Context</div><div class="car-step-title">The situation</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-2')"><div class="car-step-label">02 · Action</div><div class="car-step-title">What I did</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-pocn-3')"><div class="car-step-label">03 · Result</div><div class="car-step-title">What it produced</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div id="car-pocn-1" class="car-content">
          <div class="car-content-label">01 · Context</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">A narrow clinical audience, fixed KPI benchmarks, and an MLR-gated creative pipeline.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">POCN connects pharmaceutical brands with Nurse Practitioner and Physician Assistant audiences. Campaigns spanned 50+ therapies for J&amp;J, Eli Lilly, AbbVie, and Regeneron. Every asset moved through MLR review before deployment, audience pools were small, and KPI targets were set by the client up front — so success wasn't about chasing growth, it was about delivering contracted metrics more efficiently each cycle.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-pocn-2" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">02 · Action</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Sole programmatic operator across 30+ concurrent campaigns, plus a full DSP migration.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Owned setup, pacing, and optimization across up to 30 concurrent campaigns spanning multiple therapeutic areas — segmenting NP and PA audiences for precision targeting and tightening spend continuously against fixed benchmarks. Mid-engagement, led the migration off a third-party DSP onto a proprietary internal platform, working between Product, Engineering, and the white-label vendor to surface real operator feedback and ship usability improvements.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-pocn-3" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">03 · Result</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">$1.7M+ managed, $200K+ in annual platform cost eliminated, KPIs held throughout.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Over 26 months, delivered consistent at-or-under-budget performance against contracted KPIs across the full portfolio. The DSP migration eliminated $200K+ in annual platform license costs with zero performance disruption, while improving operational control and campaign scalability. Performance gains came from improved targeting precision and continuous optimization — not increased spend.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</CaseStudy>
